snippet.title: Monster System Reveal | Untamed Isles | Upcoming Monster Taming MMORPG
snippet.description:
Untamed Isles monsters revealed

This is pre-alpha footage, we are excited to show you all where is at and welcome all feedback and comments.

Let us know what you think!

Join us on discord to get involved in our community and participate in the upcoming giveaways and other promotions.

Untamed Isles Website: https://untamedisles.com/
Untamed Isles Discord: https://discord.gg/untamedislesofficial
Untamed Isles on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1823300/Untamed_Isles/

More Development Progress videos: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLsKxnubIJhH_zRcLdYrZB3_yA9OyG0R9K

#untamedisles #gaming #monstertaming
